# No Uppercase Text

Never render text in all caps. Avoid `text-transform: uppercase`, Tailwind's `uppercase` class, and manually writing strings in ALL CAPS.

Use normal sentence or title case instead.

```tsx
// bad
<span className="uppercase">Financial Profile</span>
<span style={{ textTransform: "uppercase" }}>Section</span>

// good
<span>Financial Profile</span>
```
